1
00:01:14,599 --> 00:01:15,879
I lost control last night.

2
00:01:16,959 --> 00:01:18,519
That woman should be awake.

3
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:45,200
I was just defending myself.

4
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,040
I won't hurt you again.

5
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:51,439
It was an unusual situation.

6
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:55,599
Don't tell me what I saw was an illusion.

7
00:01:58,719 --> 00:02:00,120
I'm sure it was real.

8
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,759
You're not human,

9
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,240
are you?

10
00:02:13,719 --> 00:02:14,680
This isn't a desert island.

11
00:02:15,039 --> 00:02:16,000
It's a meteorite

12
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,080
that fell into the ocean.

13
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,400
Over millions of years,

14
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,680
it evolved vegetation

15
00:02:22,199 --> 00:02:22,840
and soil.

16
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,240
We settled here,

17
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,400
built homes,

18
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,800
just like you.

19
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:31,199
Your ancestors were wolves.

20
00:02:32,159 --> 00:02:33,439
Affected by the tide,

21
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,599
you reveal your nature when the moon is full,

22
00:02:35,759 --> 00:02:36,800
even losing control of your powers.

23
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,560
So, Miss Jiang,

24
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:40,159
you really are a biologist.

25
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,919
Who lied to you?

26
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:44,479
The Classic of Mountains and Rivers recorded the divine dog Panhu.

27
00:02:44,879 --> 00:02:46,840
He married a princess and had descendants.

28
00:02:47,199 --> 00:02:48,199
The male descendants are dogs,

29
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:49,560
and the female are beauties.

30
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,439
I'm not a dog.

31
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,439
You just carry people away when you don't get along.

32
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,840
As you can see,

33
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:07,240
our bodies are different from ordinary people.

34
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,360
So,

35
00:03:08,879 --> 00:03:11,199
you want your people to live a civilized life

36
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,599
and not be disturbed,

37
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:15,080
So you spread the rumor that you are the boss of the gang.

38
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,039
Yes.

39
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:17,479
So yesterday

40
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:18,719
was a misunderstanding.

41
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:24,159
Ms Jiang

42
00:03:25,479 --> 00:03:26,840
I can agree to your request.

43
00:03:27,639 --> 00:03:28,759
But there is a premise.

44
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,120
What?

45
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:35,719
You have never seen me in your life.

46
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:37,599
Right?

47
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:40,919
Of course.

48
00:03:42,319 --> 00:03:42,680
Deal.

49
00:03:42,719 --> 00:03:43,120
Wait.

50
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:45,840
I have another debt to settle.

51
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:46,719
What?

52
00:03:51,159 --> 00:03:51,960
You bit me.

53
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:53,879
I...

54
00:03:55,439 --> 00:03:56,719
I lost my mind at that time.

55
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:58,719
I'm sorry.

56
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:00,719
Is that all?

57
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:44,399
Thank you.

58
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,439
Where is he?

59
00:04:52,399 --> 00:04:52,879
Sir,

60
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:53,959
what happened?

61
00:04:54,639 --> 00:04:55,319
We can help you.

62
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,399
I just kissed someone.

63
00:04:59,040 --> 00:04:59,639
This...

64
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:00,800
We can't help.

65
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:02,879
I was being treated,

66
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,439
but the wound didn't heal.

67
00:05:06,439 --> 00:05:07,519
Instead, it became

68
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:11,240
a scar.

69
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:21,000
The place where he kissed me

70
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,800
is burning like an iron.

71
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:41,279
Can he fly?

72
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,360
My heart beats fast.

73
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:02,160
[and my temperature is also very high.]

74
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,240
[My only memory of childhood,]

75
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:18,600
[the golden-eyed dog was not a dream,]

76
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:19,680
[but real.]

77
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,560
[Why do I feel]

78
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,560
[an uncontrollable burning sensation?]

79
00:06:52,439 --> 00:06:54,079
[Could it be the ancient legend's]

80
00:06:55,319 --> 00:06:56,319
[wolf clan's mark?]

81
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:58,040
You don't know me.

82
00:06:59,879 --> 00:07:01,439
Have we

83
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,959
met before?

84
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,319
[Legend has it that]

85
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,920
the one with the mark

86
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,639
will become the lifelong

87
00:07:21,959 --> 00:07:22,680
mate.

88
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:31,079
You run so fast that you need to drive.

89
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,639
I'll make you sick if I carry you all the way.

90
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:35,680
You have a conscience.

91
00:07:35,759 --> 00:07:37,199
My sense of smell is a hundred times more sensitive than yours.

92
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,759
It will stink

93
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,800
if you throw up on me.

94
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,240
But not much.

95
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,720
Your business is an amusement park.

96
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:10,680
Are they ordinary people or wolves?

97
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:11,399
Both.

98
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,600
How can I tell them apart?

99
00:08:18,199 --> 00:08:18,839
I see.

100
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:21,839
There were only wolves here.

101
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:24,040
When humans found it,

102
00:08:24,639 --> 00:08:26,120
I made it a theme park.

103
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,000
We are nocturnal.

104
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,959
We stay at home during the day.

105
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,480
At night,

106
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,480
we come out to have fun.

107
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:36,320
What do you mean by "have fun"?

108
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,840
You know a lot about wild animals.

109
00:08:48,519 --> 00:08:50,399
They have specific activity areas nearby.

110
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,120
You are safe here.

111
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:54,960
If you encounter any problems, call the security.

112
00:08:55,759 --> 00:08:56,360
He can hear you.

113
00:08:56,519 --> 00:08:57,080
What about you?

114
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,399
I'm very busy.

115
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:02,759
But you promised to be my research subject.

116
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,840
Now you're leaving me alone in the wolf's den.

117
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:07,120
It's just for your convenience.

118
00:09:09,639 --> 00:09:10,159
And

119
00:09:11,759 --> 00:09:12,559
if you're hungry,

120
00:09:16,279 --> 00:09:17,840
let's have a meal together.

121
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:18,840
No need.

122
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,200
I can go without food for a week.

123
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:29,559
[So rude.]

124
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:31,759
[He's deliberately avoiding me.]

125
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:33,639
[He must be hiding something.]

126
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:36,720
Wang, ice water.

127
00:09:44,759 --> 00:09:45,200
My lord,

128
00:09:45,919 --> 00:09:47,240
you just defied Miss Jiang,

129
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:48,440
causing the mark to backfire

130
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,679
and making you burn with pain.

131
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,320
I'll have Zhang and Li bring her back.

132
00:09:54,799 --> 00:09:56,080
I don't want to see her again.

133
00:10:03,759 --> 00:10:05,559
The Li family won't let me set up an altar for my mother,

134
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:11,000
so I have to worship her secretly.

135
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:13,559
Cang Feng,

136
00:10:14,799 --> 00:10:16,440
you must keep this a secret for me.

137
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:17,720
Yes.

138
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:19,679
From now on,

139
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,759
the only person in the world who loves me

140
00:10:22,519 --> 00:10:24,200
and protects me is gone.

141
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,759
I promised your mother

142
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,559
to protect you for life.

143
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:31,840
If I break my promise,

144
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,720
I will suffer from the pain of fire burning my skin

145
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,360
and be bitten by ants.

146
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,279
I swear on my blood.

147
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:41,840
It's unbreakable.

148
00:10:58,519 --> 00:10:59,679
No way.

149
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,399
What can I do for you?

150
00:11:08,159 --> 00:11:09,399
I don't eat pre-made food.

151
00:11:09,799 --> 00:11:11,120
I want freshly cooked food.

152
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:13,600
Sir,

153
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,559
we only provide fast food here.

154
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,159
If you don't want to eat,

155
00:11:17,759 --> 00:11:18,879
you can cook it yourself in the kitchen.

156
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,080
Cook myself?

157
00:11:23,559 --> 00:11:24,240
You cook?

158
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,840
I work for Qin Yeren.

159
00:11:30,799 --> 00:11:31,679
What?

160
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,840
I'll smash your restaurant.

161
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:36,759
I don't believe it.

162
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:38,960
Try it.

163
00:11:41,039 --> 00:11:42,480
You want to be a hero, right?

164
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:44,840
You're just a kitten.

165
00:11:45,919 --> 00:11:46,559
I...

166
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:49,200
Before you make trouble in someone else's turf,

167
00:11:49,399 --> 00:11:50,519
look at yourself first.

168
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,080
Thank you.

169
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:01,559
It's nothing.

170
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:02,600
I'm off work.

171
00:12:02,879 --> 00:12:03,519
If you're free,

172
00:12:03,879 --> 00:12:04,840
I can buy you a drink.

173
00:12:07,759 --> 00:12:09,039
Okay, see you next time.

174
00:12:10,159 --> 00:12:11,320
I mean,

175
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,159
welcome to come here next time.

176
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:16,320
Okay, I'm leaving.

177
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,200
I have something to do.
